- [ ] Configure app metadata (name, icon, appId, productName).
- [ ] Configure platform targets:
  - [ ] Windows installer (NSIS)
  - [ ] macOS dmg/pkg (later milestone)
  - [ ] Linux AppImage/deb (later milestone)
- [ ] Ensure Next production assets are bundled and reachable in packaged app.
- [ ] Add code-signing placeholders and env var docs.
- [ ] Produce internal release checklist for QA signoff.

## 12) Testing and verification
- [ ] Add minimum automated checks:
  - [ ] typecheck (`npx tsc --noEmit`)
  - [ ] lint (`npm run lint`)
  - [ ] repository/service tests
  - [ ] smoke E2E: app boots, login works, CRUD works
- [ ] Add focused manual QA script per module (patients, consultations, calendar, revenue).
- [ ] Add migration test: fresh install and upgrade from previous DB schema.

## 13) Incremental delivery plan
- [ ] M1: Electron shell + existing UI loaded (no DB rewrite yet).
- [ ] M2: SQLite + repositories + IPC read operations.
- [ ] M3: write operations + form validation + error handling.
- [ ] M4: auth/session redesign + route guards.
- [ ] M5: packaging + installer + release checklist.

